主要使用前两种
TcpServer
    This uses the Internet Tcp

UdpServer
    This uses the Internet Udp

UnixStreamServer

UnixDatagramServer

BaseServer
     |
     |
     ˇ
TcpServer ——————> UnixStreamServer
     |
     |
     ˇ
UdpServer ——————> UnixDatagramServer


First YOU MUST CREATE A REQUEST HANDLER CLASS BY THE SUBCLASSING THE BaseRequestHandler class
and overriding its handle()

你必须自己重建请求处理类，并且继承自BaseRequestHandler，并且重写handler方法

Second ,you must instantiate one of the server classes,passing it the server's address and
the request handler class

你必须实例化TCPsever 并且传递server ip and 第一步的创建的请求处理类 给 这个TCPServer

Then you can call the handler_request() or server_forever() method of the server object to process
one or many request

server.handle_request() #处理一个请求
server.server_forever() #处理多个请求 ，永远执行

finally call server_close() to close the socket.

Base

    self.setup()
    self.handle()
    self.finally（）
